body: The one by onodera is fucking amazing. The one by kousuke is amazing as well. So perfect.

Thanks for the list of artist melfice, was really looking for the first artist.
 Also sagano yuuji is as good as ever.

This is issue is good but especially saku jirou work (continuation from last issue) is the best. Damn those FEELS. In the end I don't know if she disappeared or not. They still talk so I think she stay with him, but I'm not sure.But she is some kind of 'imaginary friend' for him the girl she new in the past. And he couldn't tell her his feeling. Sad story
